name: LetsGoDex
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: lets go dex
des: The skill provides the user with the Pokemon's type(s), as well as the information given in the Pokedex from the Nintendo Switch Lets Go Eevee and Lets Go Pikachu. The app only contains the information for the Pokemon that were included in this version of the game. All the skill requires is an Alexa voice device.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
